	   <tr><td colspan=2>Quests aren't done just by GMs.&nbsp;&nbsp;There is a staff of employees dedicated to performing at least 5 quests a week on every server.  GMs and Guides help with that.  You may not see every quest, because there are so many zones and only so many helpers.<br><br>There is also a staff of Dev Team members and volunteers who do nothing but spread the story of Norrath throughout the game.  They aren't there for phat lewt, they are there to make the world a better place for RP.  So don't attack every mob you see without at least listening :)<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
